lead_paragraph: Coach Steve Kerr may be apprehensive, believing his Golden State Warriors may need a mental and physical break before the playoffs start more than chasing the record for most wins in a season.

headline.print_headline: Warriors' Young Stars Embrace Chance at Record 73 Wins
